/*

	ofxSkinnable addon
	by Ben McChesney of Helios Interactive , San Francisco CA
	
*/

This library was created solve some problems : 

Laying out buttons and UI elements from a design


Giving Designers access to this tool for detailed typography adjustments


Each scene of skinnableObjects is saved to an XML file and can be loaded into another scene.


!!! Example and Library are still under development but are in ALPHA right now !!! 

use the clone_addons.sh script for external dependencies but they are : 


External Dependencies :



git clone https://github.com/HeliosInteractive/ofxTextSuite.git


git clone https://github.com/HeliosInteractive/ofxFTGL.git


git clone https://github.com/rezaali/ofxUI.git


git clone https://github.com/benMcChesney/ofxSkinnable.git


	